[odoo-i18n] New JavaScript file created. i18n in JS:

// Odoo 16 / 17 / 18 / 19
import { _t } from "@web/core/l10n/translation";
const msg = _t("Hello World");

// Odoo 14 / 15 (legacy)
import { _t } from "web.core";

- Do NOT use f-strings or concatenation inside _t()
- Run /i18n-extract after adding _t() calls to update .po files
